</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-jHkVzv iFnjrD pf-24_ pf-text-1">The economic cost of substance misuse to society is estimated to be billions of pounds annually, encompassing healthcare, criminal justice, and lost productivity.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-jHkVzv iFnjrD pf-26_ pf-text-1">Substance misuse can lead to various health problems, including addiction, mental health disorders, and increased risk of accidents and injuries.






























































